node.title: One person dead after car rolls on highway north of Wellington
node.description: The man's vehicle blocked both lanes of State Highway 59 near Pukerua Bay.
node.content: ["A man is dead after a serious crash that has closed the main highway near Pukerua Bay, north of Wellington.", "Police said a vehicle had rolled and blocked both lanes of State Highway 59 at about 10:30am. Emergency services responded to the crash shortly before 11am, but the driver died at the scene.", "Only one vehicle was involved in the crash.", "The road is expected to be closed for some time.", "The crash was on the stretch of road known as Centennial Highway, which used to be State Highway 1 but was recently renamed to State Highway 59 in anticipation of the opening of Transmission Gully.", "There are diversions in place using Grays Road and Paek\u0101k\u0101riki Hill Road, but Waka Kotahi warned motorists to expect significant delays.", "The Paek\u0101k\u0101riki Hill Road is not suitable for heavy vehicles.", "RNZ"]
